ern Alterität ins Zentrum der Diskussion stellt.  aWe are infinitely responsible for others - ethical inter-subjectivity according to Lévinas.  afunded by AStA der Universität Oldenburg  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAlterität. 4aEmmanuel Lévinas. 4aJudith Butler. 4aMigration. 4aPhilosophie. 4aPhänomenologie. 4aPoststrukturalismus. 4aSozialität. 4aSozialphilosophie. 4aVerantwortung. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Social.2bisacsh  aEmmanuel Lévinas.  aJudith Butler.  aMigration.  aPhenomenology.  aPhilosophy.  aPost-structuralism.  aResponsibility.  aSocial Philosophy.  aSocial Relations.2 aAStA der Universität Oldenburgefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2018z9783110603217oZDB-23-DPH40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839442098zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839442098423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839442098/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPHb2018